dialog-modal-component-info.html.source:
{{title}}

By default all your models inherit from _Component. It adds to your models a set of APIs to:

- manage the component lifecycle and

- require components.

You can remove this inheritance for your needs.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>{{name}}</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <!-- system -->
  <link rel="system" type="application/json" href="{{name}}.json">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- system runtime  -->
  <script log="{{logLevel}}" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/system-runtime/dist/system-runtime.js"></script>
</body>

</html>

export-app.html.source:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>{{name}}</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- system runtime  -->
  <script log="{{logLevel}}" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/system-runtime/dist/system-runtime.js"></script>
  <!-- system -->
  <script>
    runtime.on('ready', function ready() {
        // install and start the system
        this.install({{system}});
    }, false, true);
  </script>
</body>

</html>
